---
/**
 * Stats.astro + the <Stat> pattern.
 *
 * The row of large figures in "The Moment" (e.g. 60–73% / 90% / 4 in 5).
 * <Stats> is the flex row; each <Stat> is a big blue figure with a small
 * caption underneath. Captions may contain a linked footnote.
 *
 * Usage in MDX:
 *   <Stats>
 *     <Stat figure="60–73%" caption="of enterprise data goes unused" href="https://…" />
 *   </Stats>
 */
---
<div class="wp-stats">
  <slot />
</div>
